- AN OLD FAIRY?

27:19.906 --> 27:21.407
IT'S CALLED FAIRY POWER.

27:21.440 --> 27:26.278
IT'S WHAT GIVES US
OUR WILL TO SURVIVE.

27:26.312 --> 27:29.916
BUT SOMETIMES,
WE FORGET WE HAVE IT.

27:32.218 --> 27:35.054
THAT'S WHY THE GATHERING
WAS STARTED,

27:35.087 --> 27:39.158
TO HELP US REMEMBER,
TO CELEBRATE.

27:39.191 --> 27:44.030
- THAT'S WHY I CAME,
TO RENEW MY SPIRIT, YOU KNOW?

27:44.063 --> 27:46.032
