42:06.925 --> 42:10.696
I'D STILL REMEMBER
WHAT I DID.

42:10.729 --> 42:15.033
GOD, HOW I HURT
THE PEOPLE THAT I LOVED.

42:15.066 --> 42:18.003
- YOU GOING TO BE
ALL RIGHT?

42:22.808 --> 42:26.177
- WELL, TELL YOU THE TRUTH,
AFTER REHAB,

42:26.211 --> 42:28.814
WHERE THEY NEVER LEFT YOU ALONE,
I'M-I'M-I'M FEELING

42:28.847 --> 42:32.350
