BEING HERE BY MYSELF.

42:32.383 --> 42:35.120
- I, UH, COULD STAY WITH YOU,
IF YOU'D LIKE.

42:35.153 --> 42:37.656
- OH, NO.
I-I-I COULDN'T ASK--

42:37.689 --> 42:39.958
- IF IT'D MAKE YOU FEEL BETTER.
[chuckles]

42:39.991 --> 42:45.697
- UM...WELL, UH...

42:45.731 --> 42:47.198
WHERE DO WE--I MEAN--

42:47.232 --> 42:50.101
- I'D CRASH ON THE SOFA.

42:50.135 --> 42:53.939
- YEAH, THE SOFA.
RIGHT, UM...

42:53.972 --> 42:57.242
OF COURSE.
I'LL GET YOU SOME BLANKETS.

43:26.071 --> 43:27.405
SLEEP TIGHT.

43:27.438 --> 43:29.374
- YEAH, YOU TOO.

43:29.407 --> 43:34.312
AND, UH...
IF YOU NEED ANYTHING, UH--

43:52.430 --> 43:55.000
- I FEEL THE POWER.

43:55.033 --> 43:58.203
[coyote barking]

43:58.236 --> 44:01.807
- I FEEL THE POWER.

44:01.840 --> 44:05.143
- I FEEL THE POWER TOO.

44:05.176 --> 44:07.746
- NOW, LET US STOKE
OUR FIRES

44:07.779 --> 44:10.181
AND RELEASE OUR BURDENS
INTO THE FLAMES.

44:10.215 --> 44:12.417
- HOLD IT!

44:12.450 --> 44:17.288
I'LL TAKE THAT, DUMPLING.
- HEY.

44:17.322 --> 44:21.359
- I FEEL THE POWER TOO.

44:21.392 --> 44:25.831
MY NAME IS, UH, "ON A CLEAR DAY,
YOU CAN SEE FOREVER."

44:25.864 --> 44:29.167
IT JUST SORT OF CAME TO ME,
KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

44:29.200 --> 44:32.203
BUT YOU CAN CALL ME
"CLEAR DAY."

44:32.237 --> 44:34.172
[murmuring]

44:34.205 --> 44:36.174
- THIS IS A HEART CIRCLE,
CLEAR DAY.

44:36.207 --> 44:38.710
WE SHARE OUR FEELINGS HERE.

44:38.744 --> 44:40.445
IS THERE ANYTHING
YOU'D LIKE TO SHARE?

44:40.478 --> 44:43.849
- WELL...

44:43.882 --> 44:48.319
THE TRUTH IS, I DIDN'T REALLY
WANT TO COME HERE.

44:48.353 --> 44:51.957
BUT THEN, SOMEHOW,

44:51.990 --> 44:54.926
SOMETHING MAGICAL HAPPENED.

44:54.960 --> 44:58.864
[murmuring agreement]
- ALWAYS DOES.

44:58.897 --> 45:03.034
- I REALIZED THAT IF IT'S TRUE
THAT FAIRIES HAVE THE POWER

45:03.068 --> 45:06.071
TO CREATE BEAUTY
OUT OF UGLINESS

45:06.104 --> 45:09.407
AND JOY OUT OF PAIN,

45:09.440 --> 45:13.111
THEN THAT POWER
CAN ONLY COME FROM ONE PLACE.

45:13.144 --> 45:14.946
- MM-HMM.

45:14.980 --> 45:19.284
- WHICH I-I GUESS
I KNEW ALL ALONG.

45:24.122 --> 45:26.892
- THANK YOU.

45:26.925 --> 45:28.860
RISE, FAIRIES.

45:32.898 --> 45:35.533
WE THANK THE POWERS OF THE EARTH
AND THE HEAVENS

45:35.566 --> 45:38.503
FOR GIVING US
OUR SPECIAL GIFTS.

45:38.536 --> 45:40.872
WE CELEBRATE
OUR FAIRY FOREFATHERS

45:40.906 --> 45:43.975
AND THE GENERATIONS
OF FAIRIES TO FOLLOW,

45:44.009 --> 45:47.979
AND OUR FAIRY FOUNDER,
HARRY HAY.

45:48.013 --> 45:49.848
[all murmur]

45:49.881 --> 45:52.851
- WHERE IS HE, ANYWAY?
- HARRY HAY?

45:52.884 --> 45:55.987
- YEAH, I HELPED HIM
PUT THE ROCKS IN THE CIRCLE.

45:56.021 --> 46:01.159
- HONEY, HARRY PASSED AWAY
TWO YEARS AGO.

46:12.070 --> 46:13.872
